# mogura clean 示範:掃描進度 → 攤開清單 → 勾選 → 離開(不實際刪除)
Output demo/clean.gif

Set FontSize 15
Set Width 1100
Set Height 640
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 60ms
Set Padding 12

Env MOGURA_LANG "en"

Type "mogura"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 5s

Down@250ms 2
Space
Sleep 800ms
Down@250ms 1
Space
Sleep 1.2s
Down@250ms 2
Sleep 800ms

Type "q"
Sleep 1s
